snippet.title: Amber Heard's Former Assistant Exposes Her
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Former Assistant Exposes Her 
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

Amber heard’s ex assistant Kate James has spoken out in a legal declaration gearing up to Johnny Depps’ 50 million dollar defamation lawsuit against amber. The short version is, she had a lot of bad things to say about amber and a lot of nice things to say about johnny. I’m going to tell you all the details of this deposition, right now on IO.
